highlights.text: “Te Felicito” by Shakira and Rauw Alejandro is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 112 spots at #79.
“Flowers” by Miley Cyrus is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #1.
The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Creepin' (with The Weeknd & 21 Savage)” is the highest at #4.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 311 weeks straight.
